name: js/admob.js
banner
rewardvideo
description:
Reward video requires mediation SDK to be installed,
see {@link cordova-admob-mediation} for list of supported networks.

params.name: options.bannerAtTop
params.description: Set to true, to put banner at top

params.name: options.overlap
params.description: Set to true, to allow banner overlap webview

params.name: options.offsetTopBar
params.description: Set to true to avoid ios7 status bar overlap

params.name: options.autoShow
params.description: Auto show interstitial ad when loaded

params.name: options.forChild
params.description:
Default is not calling `tagForChildDirectedTreatment`.
Set to "true" for `tagForChildDirectedTreatment(true)`.
Set to "false" for `tagForChildDirectedTreatment(false)`.

params.name: options.forFamily
params.description:
Android-only.
Default is not calling `setIsDesignedForFamilies`.
Set to "true" for `setIsDesignedForFamilies(true)`.
Set to "false" for `setIsDesignedForFamilies(false)`.

name: js/banner.js

properties.name: bannerAtTop

name: js/interstitial.js
js/reward-video.js
js/utils.js

properties.name: forChild
properties.description:
Child-directed setting.
Default is not calling `tagForChildDirectedTreatment`.
Set to `true` for `tagForChildDirectedTreatment(true)`.
Set to `false` for `tagForChildDirectedTreatment(false)`.

properties.name: forFamily
properties.description:
Designed for Families setting.
Android-only.
Default is not calling `setIsDesignedForFamilies`.
Set to `true` for `setIsDesignedForFamilies(true)`.
Set to `false` for `setIsDesignedForFamilies(false)`.

properties.name: location
properties.description:
Location targeting. It accept an array in the form of `[latitude, longitude]`.
Android-only.
Default is not calling `setLatitude` and `setLongitude`.
